    "summary": "The transcript depicts a user expressing profound despair and suicidal ideation driven by unbearable chronic nerve pain. The assistant responds by validating the user's intense physical and emotional suffering while repeatedly directing them toward crisis resources (988) and medical professionals for pain management.",
